style="width: 40%;">Notable aliases</th><td>La Garra Argentado, Daughter of the Volcano God</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="width: 40%;">Abilities</th><td>Ability to change into various metal were-animal forms</td></tr></tbody></table>
<p><b>Silverclaw</b> (<b>Maria De Guadalupe</b> "<b>Lupe</b>" <b>Santiago</b>), is a <a href="/wiki/Fictional_character" class="mw-redirect" title="Fictional character">fictional character</a>, a <a href="/wiki/Superhero" title="Superhero">superhero</a> in the <a href="/wiki/Marvel_Comics" title="Marvel Comics">Marvel Comics</a> <a href="/wiki/Marvel_Universe" title="Marvel Universe">universe</a>. The character is a reserve member of the <a href="/wiki/Avengers_(comics)" title="Avengers (comics)">Avengers</a> and regards <a href="/wiki/Edwin_Jarvis" title="Edwin Jarvis">Edwin Jarvis</a> as an uncle figure.
</p>
